### 1. 배송 담당자 생성
POST http://localhost:8086/api/v1/delivery-drivers
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deliveryDriverId": 1,
  "hubId": "e4d5c6b7-1111-2222-3333-444444444444",
  "slackId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "driverType": "HUB"
}


### 2. 배송 담당자 전체 조회

### Test Case 1: 기본 요청 (쿼리 파라미터 없음)
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/delivery-drivers
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### Test Case 2: deliveryDriverId 필터링
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/delivery-drivers?deliveryDriverId=1
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### Test Case 3: hubId와 slackId 필터링
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/delivery-drivers?hubId=e4d5c6b7-1111-2222-3333-444444444444&slackId=123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### Test Case 4: driverType 필터링 (예: HUB)
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/delivery-drivers?driverType=HUB
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### Test Case 5: 모든 필터 조건 사용 (페이지, 사이즈, 정렬 등)
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/delivery-drivers?page=2&size=5&orderBy=assignAt&sort=asc&deliveryDriverId=2&hubId=abcdefab-1111-2222-3333-444444444444&slackId=def12345-1111-2222-3333-444444444444&driverType=COMPANY&deliverySequence=3&assignAt=2025-03-23T12:10:00
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json


### 3. 배송 담당자 상세 조회 (경로 포함)
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/delivery-drivers/1
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json
